rows.label: tlk45300011_03_msg0001
rows.name:
I've been up to my eyeballs in work
lately. Haven't been giving my girl
the attention she deserves.

rows.label: tlk45300011_03_msg0002
rows.name:
She almost flipped her lid at me
the other day. I've never seen her
do that before.

rows.label: tlk45300011_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I thought I might buy her some Samod
on the way home. She loves Samod.

rows.label: tlk45300011_03_msg0004
rows.name:
It's got to be something different
from the norm, though. She's a
bit avant-garde in that respect.
